data.description: Just in time for the New Year!  Welcome Home to this beautiful home with many upgrades.  With 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, Hardwood floors, and gas fireplace, this is sure to please!  The kitchen has granite counter tops, bar area, stainless steel appliances, eat-in kitchen area with built in seating.  Primary bedroom has electric fireplace, new floors, and master bath is a complete remodel.  Custom tiled shower, tiled floor, double vanity, and barn door.  Large 4th bedroom upstairs with walk in closet and full bath.  Amazing Outdoor living space with a screen porch to watch your games, a custom built bar, large deck around above ground pool, storage under decking on back porch, and backs up to woods.  Large lot and upgrades to include: floors, roof-approx 1 year, HVAC-less than 5 years (main), gutters, sprinkler system, & multiple attic walk outs.
